April 26 shooting-death of Roy

Mr.. and Mrs. Grady Wady. ST.,
4543 E. Transmission Rd., Tenn
pc, loves scouting. Since joining
three years ago, he has kept a
high interest and recently re-
turned from a week at Camp
Geronimo.


An eighth grader at McKemy
School. he plans to be mechan-
ical engineer. Grady fixes all
sorts of broken toys and small
machines.


He was named the outstanding
Little League pitcher in 1862.


Gary is a member of Union
Baptist Church.
